{"parentUuid": "e9579523-1aa5-49d5-9453-cac58a860eea", "isSidechain": false, "type": "user", "message": {"role": "user", "content": [{"type": "tool_result", "tool_use_id": "toolu_e96e12c9-74ce-47", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "import { db } from \"@/lib/db\";\nimport { NextRequest } from \"next/server\";\n\nexport async function GET(req: NextRequest) {\n  const q = req.nextUrl.searchParams.get(\"q\") ?? \"\";\n  const results = await db.query.documents.findMany({\n    where: (doc, { ilike }) => ilike(doc.title, `%${q}%`),\n  });\n  const enriched = await Promise.all(\n    results.map(async (r) => ({\n      ...r,\n      author: await db.query.users.findFirst({ where: (u, { eq }) => eq(u.id, r.authorId) }),\n    }))\n  );\n  return Response.json(enriched);\n}\n"}]}]}, "uuid": "56aa3ece-5d83-44a1-b708-af725bae8804", "timestamp": "2026-05-13T00:00:37.000Z", "isMeta": true, "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/nextjs-app", "sessionId": "098e3e61-8963-4325-b719-0885e03d82ab", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
{"parentUuid": "56aa3ece-5d83-44a1-b708-af725bae8804", "isSidechain": false, "message": {"model": "claude-sonnet-4-6", "id": "msg_50698cf6-da4", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Classic N+1: you fetch all matching docs, then fire one `findFirst` per result to enrich the author. With 50 docs in a result page that's 51 round trips. Two fixes: (1) join in the original query \u2014 Drizzle: `with: { author: true }`; or (2) batch the author lookups with `inArray(users.id, authorIds)` and stitch in JS. The `ilike` with leading-wildcard is also non-indexable \u2014 if `documents.title` is large, add a `gin` index with `pg_trgm` and use `%>` (similarity) for true full-text-style matching."}], "stop_reason": "end_turn", "usage": {"input_tokens": 159, "output_tokens": 295, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 7020}}, "requestId": "req_8b111370-39e", "type": "assistant", "uuid": "541658a0-2c03-40d8-bcab-b1ba7b3c7613", "timestamp": "2026-05-13T00:00:43.000Z", "userType": "external", "entrypoint": "cli", "cwd": "/Users/alex/code/nextjs-app", "sessionId": "098e3e61-8963-4325-b719-0885e03d82ab", "version": "2.0.0", "gitBranch": "main"}
